{
  "text": "It has been demonstrated in many studies concerning various specialties, including occupational medicine, that the recall ratio of Medline was far from 100% [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] [CITATION_6] .",
